<title>KHRIH VAILAM AH CH133</title>
<lyrics>[V1]
 Khrih vailam kei chawrnak a si, Caan hlun chungin ka hmun ko, A thiang
 tuanbia ceunak vialte, Vailam parah an i pum.

[V2]
 Ngaihchiatnak a ka tlunh tikah, Ruahchan a lo, tih a zual, Vailam nih
 a ka hlaw lai lo, Zohhmanh, daihnak he a ceu.

[V3]
 Lunglawmhnak ni a tlan tikah, Ka lam ceu dawtnak a um, Vailam ceu
 thlam a chuakmi nih, Ni ceu kha a dawhter chin.

[V4]
 Thluachuah vanluh, sifah retheih, Vailam nih a thianter ko; Khingthlai
 khawh lo daihnak a um, A hmun zungzal lawmhnak he.</lyrics>
<key>C</key>
</song>